                {
                  "type": "text",
                  "id": "EcEzf",
                  "name": "Spec",
                  "fill": "#3D2B1F",
                  "textGrowth": "fixed-width",
                  "width": "fill_container",
                  "content": "On tap, the seal blooms with a soft sparkle and dissolves. Each garment then drifts into its flat-lay position on a gentle spring with a slight rotation settle, staggered ~70ms apart — like laying clothes out on a table, not a confetti burst. The ‘why this look’ note fades in last. Reuses the app's existing Motion spring + stagger. Subsequent shuffles skip the ceremony: the flat-lay cross-fades to the new outfit instantly, no seal and no summary.",
                  "lineHeight": 1.5,
                  "fontFamily": "DM Sans",
                  "fontSize": 13,
                  "fontWeight": "normal"
                }
              ]
            }
          ]
        }
      ]
