                  "name": "Spec",
                  "fill": "#3D2B1F",
                  "textGrowth": "fixed-width",
                  "width": "fill_container",
                  "content": "One shared wrapper on every route change: the incoming screen fades in while sliding up ~8px (~200ms, ease-out); the outgoing screen cross-fades out. Lists and grids stagger their items in rather than snapping. Under prefers-reduced-motion it falls back to an instant cross-fade. Keep it understated — the daily reveal is the only screen that earns real choreography.",
                  "lineHeight": 1.5,
                  "fontFamily": "DM Sans",
                  "fontSize": 13,
                  "fontWeight": "normal"
                }
              ]
            }
          ]
