      "id": "SPXQE",
      "x": 3600,
      "y": 1412,
      "name": "Event-chips spec note",
      "width": 360,
      "height": 170,
      "content": "DRESSING-FOR SELECTOR (KAN-92)\n\n• A compact dropdown on the Wrapped page lists the day's calendar events.\n• Default = most-formal event of the day (never underdressed).\n• Pick another → the look regenerates for that occasion.\n• No events that day → shows 'Everyday' (casual default).\n• Occasion maps Event.Type → formal / casual / sport (matches wardrobe Category)."
