      "content": "MOBILE LANDING ADAPTATIONS\n\n• Single column — hero copy then inline product card (no phone-in-phone)\n• Full-width primary CTA in hero\n• Trust items stack vertically\n• Steps use horizontal row layout (icon + text) to save height\n• Proof band stacks quote + stat vertically\n• Nav drops header Get started — one CTA in hero + footer"
